'''和平與民主黨'''（{{lang-en|Peace and Democracy Party}}，{{lang-tr|Barış ve Demokrasi Partisi}}，{{lang-ku|Partiya Aştî û Demokrasiyê}}，简称BDP）是[[土耳其|土耳其]]一个已不存在的親[[庫爾德族|庫爾德族]][[土耳其政党列表|政党]]。

== 形成 ==
前身是{{link-en|民主社会党 (土耳其)|Democratic Society Party|民主社会党}}，2008年改名，与[[库尔德工人党|库尔德工人党]]有联系。由{{link-en|萨拉丁·德米尔塔什|Selahattin Demirtaş}}和{{link-en|居尔滕·克沙纳克|Gültan Kışanak}}共同领导。

== 意识形态 ==
党主席呼吁[[库尔德工人党|库尔德工人党]]解除武装<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.todayszaman.com/news-283975-bdp-chairman-calls-on-pkk-to-lay-down-arms.html |title=BDP chairman calls on PKK to lay down arms |accessdate=2013-04-19 |archive-date=2012-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120624070403/http://www.todayszaman.com/news-283975-bdp-chairman-calls-on-pkk-to-lay-down-arms.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。BDP是[[社会党国际|社会党国际]]观察成员<ref>{{cite web |title=Member Parties of the Socialist International |url=http://www.socialistinternational.org/viewArticle.cfm?ArticlePageID=931 |publisher=[[社会党国际|社会党国际]] |access-date=2013-04-19 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20131103120922/http://www.socialistinternational.org/viewArticle.cfm?ArticlePageID=931 |archive-date=2013-11-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。BDP支持土耳其加入欧盟<ref name=aboutus>{{cite web|title=About Peace and Democracy Party|url=http://peaceandemocracy.org/about-us/about-us.html|work=BDP|publisher=BDP|accessdate=10 August 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029201609/http://peaceandemocracy.org/about-us/about-us.html|archivedate=2013年10月29日}}</ref>，支持承认同性婚姻和保护LGBT人群<ref>{{cite news|title=BDP'nin eşcinsel evlilik isteği tartışılıyor|url=http://www.haber10.com/haber/279069/#.Uga3-NLOtOY|accessdate=10 August 2013|newspaper=Haber 10|date=15 May 2013|language=tr|archive-date=2015-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150704161412/http://www.haber10.com/haber/279069/#.Uga3-NLOtOY|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并且呼吁土耳其政府承认[[亚美尼亚大屠杀|亚美尼亚大屠杀]]<ref>{{cite news|title=BDP urges Turkey to offer apology to Armenians|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/bdp-urges-turkey-to-offer-apology-to-armenians.aspx?pageID=238&nid=45534|accessdate=10 August 2013|newspaper=Hurriyet Daily News|date=14 April 2013|archive-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010113449/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/bdp-urges-turkey-to-offer-apology-to-armenians.aspx?pageID=238&nid=45534|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 選舉 ==
由於以政黨名單參加國會選舉需要在全國取得至少10%的得票率方可取得議席，在2011年國會選舉中，該黨支持的參選人以獨立人士身份報名參選，以避開上述針對政黨的門檻。

== 和人民民主黨的關係 ==
[[人民民主黨_(土耳其)|人民民主黨]]（HDP）是BDP的兄弟党。

在{{link-en|2014年土耳其地方选举|Turkish local elections, 2014}}中，BDP与HDP在库尔德人为主的土耳其东南地区联合参选，HDP在其它地区单独参选<ref name="new party">{{cite web|url=http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2013/10/new-kurdish-party-could-impact-turkey-elections.html#ixzz2tn1xudyq|title=New Kurdish Party Could Impact Local Turkish Elections|last=Cengiz|first=Orhan Kemal|coauthors=Sibel Utku Bila (translator)|date=31 October 2013|publisher=Al-Monitor|accessdate=24 February 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227105411/http://www.al-monitor.com/pulse/originals/2013/10/new-kurdish-party-could-impact-turkey-elections.html#ixzz2tn1xudyq|archivedate=2014年2月27日}}</ref>，除此之外BDP只在[[梅尔辛省|梅尔辛省]]和[[科尼亚省|科尼亚省]]推出了自己的候选人<ref>[http://www.bdp.org.tr/tr/?page_id=5050 ADAYLARIMIZ] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bdp.org.tr/tr/?page_id=5050 |date=20140308075718 }}, BDP official website</ref>。

地方选举之后，双方重组为一个联合结构。2014年4月28日BDP的整个议会党团加入HDP，而BDP专门负责地区行政层级<ref name="party">{{cite web|url=http://www.sabah.com.tr/Gundem/2014/04/28/bdp-milletvekilleri-hdpye-katildi|title=BDP milletvekilleri HDP'ye katıldı|last=|first=|date=28 April 2014|publisher=Al-Monitor|accessdate=24 February 2014|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127120932/https://www.sabah.com.tr/gundem/2014/04/28/bdp-milletvekilleri-hdpye-katildi|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://odatv.com/n.php?n=bdp-artik-mecliste-yok-2804141200 |title=BDP artık Meclis'te yok |accessdate=2015-06-08 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040145/http://odatv.com/n.php?n=bdp-artik-mecliste-yok-2804141200 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 重组 ==
2014年7月11日，在第三次大会上，该党将党名改为{{link-en|民主地區黨|Democratic Regions Party}}以表明只参与地方政府层面的活动<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.evrensel.net/haber/88097/bdpnin-adi-demokratik-bolgeler-partisi-oldu|title=BDP'nin adı Demokratik Bölgeler Partisi oldu|last=|first=|date=11 July 2014|publisher=[[Evrensel|Evrensel]]|accessdate=24 February 2015|archive-date=2018-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180810122602/https://www.evrensel.net/haber/88097/bdpnin-adi-demokratik-bolgeler-partisi-oldu|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
